[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1209","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1209.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0911","title":"ProFTPd MKD/CWD 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ProFTPd 1.2 pre1 至 pre5 版本、wu-ftpd 及 beroftpd 中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送一系列精心构造的 MKD（创建目录）和 CWD（切换目录）命令，创建深层嵌套目录结构，触发缓冲区溢出，进而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响多个主流 FTP 服务端软件，危害严重，无需认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0911"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.797","remediation":"升级 ProFTPd 至 1.2.0 RC1 或更高稳定版本（1.2.0pre 系列已停止支持），该漏洞在 1.2.0 RC1 中修复。使用 wu-ftpd 的用户应升级至 2.6.2 或更新版本，或在 inetd 配置中禁用匿名用户 MKD/CWD 目录创建权限作为临时缓解措施。beroftpd 用户建议迁移至已维护的 FTP 服务器软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/1999/19990210","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/612","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19476"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1209.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1208","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1208.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0909","title":"Microsoft Windows 多宿主系统 IP 源路由绕过漏洞","description":"Windows 98 SE、Windows NT、Windows 95 及 Terminal Server 等多宿主 Windows 系统存在安全绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的包含 IP 选项的畸形数据包，绕过 IP 源路由限制，从而实施网络劫持或中间人攻击。该漏洞影响多款早期 Windows 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0909"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.537","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-038 提供的补丁程序，该补丁修复了 IP 源路由绕过漏洞，并新增通过注册表 DisableIPSourceRouting (HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\Tcpip\\Parameters) 设为 2 以完全禁用源路由的功能。由于 Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 均已停止支持且不再接收更新，建议尽快升级到受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016+），同时在网络边界防火墙和路由器上配置策略丢弃带有 IP 源路由选项（Loose Source Route 和 Strict Source Route）的入站数据包作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ238453","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/646","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-038"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1208.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1200","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1200.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0896","title":"RealNetworks RealServer 管理工具缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"RealNetworks RealServer 管理工具中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向该工具的管理接口提交超长的用户名和密码参数触发缓冲区溢出，进而导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 RealNetworks RealServer 多个版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0896"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.937","remediation":"立即升级 RealNetworks RealServer 至 G2 版本或更高版本，该版本修复了管理后台认证过程中的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，应在防火墙层面限制对 RealServer 管理端口（默认 9090/TCP 和 9091/TCP）的访问，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 连接，并在输入验证层面限制用户名和密码字段长度。鉴于该产品已停止技术支持，建议迁移至更现代且受支持的流媒体服务器产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://service.real.com/help/faq/servg260.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/767","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19593"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1200.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1198","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1198.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0894","title":"Red Hat Linux screen 程序本地终端写入漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 的 screen 终端复用程序未使用 Unix98 伪终端（ptys），导致其创建的终端会话缺乏必要的权限隔离机制。本地攻击者可通过向其他用户使用的 screen 终端写入数据，实现会话劫持或任意命令注入。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 多个版本，利用前提是攻击者拥有本地系统账户，攻击复杂度低，危害等级为高危。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0894"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.680","remediation":"升级 Red Hat Linux 至 6.2 及以上版本（默认启用 Unix98 ptys），或单独升级 screen 程序至 3.07.06 及以上版本。如无法升级，在 screen 配置文件中添加 `defunix98 on` 启用 Unix98 pty 支持，并限制本地非信任用户登录系统以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0894"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1198.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1168","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1168.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0886","title":"Microsoft Windows NT RASMAN 权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的远程访问服务管理器（RASMAN）存在安全描述符配置缺陷，允许本地用户通过服务控制管理器将 RASMAN 指向备用位置，从而以 SYSTEM 权限执行任意代码。攻击者需具有本地登录权限，利用该配置漏洞可完全控制受影响的 Windows NT 4.0 系统（包括 SP1~SP6 版本），实现权限提升。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0886"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:15.700","remediation":"最彻底的解决方案是升级至受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022），Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持且不再发布安全更新。如无法升级，可禁用 Remote Access Service（RAS）服务，并修改注册表中 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\RASMAN 项的权限，仅允许 Administrators 组访问，同时通过组策略限制非授权用户对服务控制管理器的操作。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ242294","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/645","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-041","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19502"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1168.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1111","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1111.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0883","title":"Zeus Web Server 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Zeus Web Server 存在任意文件读取漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向搜索功能传递包含文件名的选项参数，绕过访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露（如配置文件、密码文件等）。该漏洞影响 Zeus Web Server 多个版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议升级至最新版本或禁用搜索功能以降低风险。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0883"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:15.327","remediation":"升级至 Zeus Web Server 3.1 及以上版本，该版本已修复通过搜索引擎选项读取任意文件的问题。若无法升级，在 Zeus 配置中禁用搜索功能（移除或注释 search 指令），并限制 Web 服务进程的文件系统访问权限，确保其仅能读取网站根目录下的文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1126","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/742","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3380"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1111.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1109","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1109.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0879","title":"Washington University WU-FTPD message 文件宏变量远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Washington University WU-FTPD 2.5.0 在处理 message 文件中的宏变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的 message 文件触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，从而在受影响系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 WU-FTPD 2.5.0 及相关 FTP 服务器软件，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。管理员应立即升级至修复版本或应用厂商提供的安全补丁。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0879"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.873","remediation":"升级 WU-FTPD 至 2.6.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了 message 文件宏变量处理中的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，可禁用 FTP 服务的 message 功能（删除/etc/ftpaccess 中相关 message 指令），并在防火墙限制对 21 端口的访问以缩小攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0879","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19560"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1109.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1108","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1108.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0878","title":"WU-FTPD 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"WU-FTPD 及其相关 FTP 服务器中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务发送特制的 MAPPING_CHDIR 命令触发该漏洞，导致越界内存写入并最终获取系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响大量使用 WU-FTPD 的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，无需认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0878"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.740","remediation":"建议立即升级 WU-FTPD 至 2.6.0 及以上版本（该漏洞已在后续版本中修复），或迁移至 vsftpd、ProFTPD 等仍在积极维护的 FTP 服务端。如无法升级，可在 inetd.conf 中禁用 FTP 服务，改用 SFTP/SCP 替代文件传输协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/599"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1108.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1106","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1106.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0876","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.0 在处理 EMBED 标签时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可构造包含超长 EMBED 标签属性的恶意 HTML 页面，当用户使用 IE 4.0 访问该页面时触发缓冲区溢出，导致攻击者可在当前用户上下文中执行任意代码，完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上使用 IE 4.0 的所有版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0876"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.490","remediation":"立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 4.01 Service Pack 2 及以上版本，该版本修复了 EMBED 标签解析时的缓冲区溢出漏洞。对于当前仍在使用旧版 IE 的环境，建议升级至受支持的现代浏览器（如 Microsoft Edge），并禁用已停止维护的 IE 浏览器中 ActiveX 及 EMBED 标签的调用权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ185959","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q176/6/97.asp"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1100","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1100.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0875","title":"Microsoft Windows 98/Solaris IRDP 默认路由欺骗漏洞","description":"Windows 98a/98b/98SE 及 Solaris 2.6 系统中启用了 ICMP 路由器发现协议（IRDP）的 DHCP 客户端存在路由欺骗漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标主机发送伪造的 ICMP 路由器通告报文，即可篡改其默认网关路由表条目，将网络流量劫持至攻击者控制的路径上，导致中间人攻击、数据窃听或流量拦截。该漏洞利用门槛低，攻击者仅需与目标在同一广播域内即可实施。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0875"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.373","remediation":"Windows 98 系统通过修改注册表禁用 IRDP：在 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\System\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\VxD\\MSTCP 下新建 DWORD 值 PerformRouterDiscovery=0。Solaris 2.6 系统执行 ndd -set /dev/ip ip_forward_directed_broadcasts 0 并修改 /etc/init.d/inetinit 添加 ndd -set /dev/ip ip_ignore_redirect 1。网络层可在边界防火墙上过滤 ICMP Router Advertisement（类型 9）和 Router Solicitation（类型 10）报文阻断攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ216141","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/578","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19451"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1100.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1051","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1051.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1335","title":"Red Hat Linux cmu-snmp snmpd 配置错误漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 4.0 系统中 cmu-snmp 软件包 3.3-1 之前版本的 snmpd 服务器存在配置错误漏洞。由于默认配置不当，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞对目标系统上的敏感信息进行读取或写入操作，导致信息泄露或系统配置被篡改。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 4.0 及使用相关 cmu-snmp 组件的系统，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1335"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.290","remediation":"升级 cmu-snmp 软件包至 3.3-1 或更高版本，并修改 SNMP 配置文件 /etc/snmp/snmpd.conf，将默认 public/private 团体字改为复杂随机字符串；同时在 iptables 防火墙中限制仅信任 IP 可访问 UDP 161 端口，禁用 SNMP 写权限（read-only）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh40-errata-general.html#cmu-snmp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7251","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1335","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1335.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pr33-x2p7-6w2x/GHSA-pr33-x2p7-6w2x.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001032.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--54c919b9-3bdc-4906-ba93-56a73c55a239.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1051.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1050","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1050.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1334","title":"Elm 2.4 filter 缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"Elm 2.4 邮件客户端的 filter 命令存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向受害者发送包含超长 From: 或 Reply-To: 头的恶意邮件，或诱使用户以超长 -f 参数运行 filter 命令，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Elm 2.4 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1334"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.147","remediation":"升级 Elm 到 2.4.5 或更高版本，该版本修复了 filter 命令中的缓冲区溢出问题。Red Hat 在 RH50 errata 中发布了针对 elm 的安全更新。如无法升级，建议禁用 filter 命令或避免使用 Elm 处理不可信来源的邮件，同时可考虑迁移至现代邮件客户端如 Thunderbird 或 Mutt。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88609666024181&w=2","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#elm","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1334.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1334","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1334.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9pwm-wh34-fpxm/GHSA-9pwm-wh34-fpxm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001031.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1334.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1050.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1047","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1047.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1331","title":"Red Hat Linux netcfg 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 4.2 中的 netcfg 2.16-1 网络配置工具存在安全配置缺陷，当特定选项被设置后，系统重启时以太网接口的控制权会被不当授予普通用户。本地攻击者可利用此漏洞在未授权的情况下关闭网络接口，导致目标系统失去网络连接能力，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 4.2 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，攻击前提是攻击者拥有本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1331"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:12.733","remediation":"升级 netcfg 至修复版本，或应用 Red Hat RH42 errata 中针对 netcfg 的安全更新。该漏洞在 Red Hat Linux 4.2 的 netcfg 2.16-1 中存在，建议禁用 netcfg 的自动接口控制选项作为临时缓解。对于已停止支持的旧版本，建议迁移至现代受支持的 RHEL 发行版（如 RHEL 7/8/9），并确保网络管理组件保持最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7245.php","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh42-errata-general.html#netcfg","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1331.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1331","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1331.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1331.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qcqp-mmmc-3pj9/GHSA-qcqp-mmmc-3pj9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84435/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1331.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ad7c142ce47bdca962dc5352eae3764ce44639d2/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1047.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1045","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1045.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1329","title":"Red Hat Linux SysVInit 缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.1 及更早版本中的 SysVInit 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过向 SysVInit 发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 5.1 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。由于攻击者需要本地访问权限，攻击门槛较高，但一旦利用成功可完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1329"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:12.473","remediation":"升级至 Red Hat Linux 5.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 SysVInit 缓冲区溢出问题。对于已停止支持的旧版本，建议迁移至现代受支持的 RHEL 发行版（如 RHEL 7/8/9），并确保系统初始化组件保持最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7250.php","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#SysVinit","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1329.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1329","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1329.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1329.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vcmw-4q9q-gx59/GHSA-vcmw-4q9q-gx59.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83032/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1329.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ad7c142ce47bdca962dc5352eae3764ce44639d2/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1045.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1043","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1043.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0698","title":"Red Hat IP Protocol Logger 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Red Hat 和 Debian Linux 系统中 IP 协议日志记录工具 ippl 存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制数据包，触发 ippl 日志处理异常，导致系统资源耗尽或服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 及 Debian Linux 多个版本，攻击复杂度低，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0698"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.313","remediation":"立即停止并禁用 ippl 服务（`systemctl stop ippl && systemctl disable ippl`），或卸载 ippl 软件包（`apt-get remove ippl` 或 `rpm -e ippl`）。对于仍在运行的 Red Hat/Debian 系统，建议升级到包含修复的最新版本或迁移到受支持的发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0698","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0698.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0698","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0698.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0698.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f8vp-pmch-x64j/GHSA-f8vp-pmch-x64j.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0698.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88102/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--71ae6621-e6c7-4f99-8831-7f508bac1ca3.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/linux.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1043.toml"}]